  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Ballad",
    "Ambient"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 3,
  "lyrics": "Sometimes you need a little one Sometimes you need someone to pull your string and watch you unravel inside of your own dreams to keep you honest keep you working hard to fear you can't be dishonest you can't be hard you can't lie to yourself when you think you can't make it past what they won't put in front of you are you gonna be cold are you gonna grow old and dim your lights and dim your pipes and dim everything inside your right to call yourself you are you cold you little heat inside of us all are you bold are you cold are you bold when you pull the string and watch it all unravel will you watch others grow not stunt not fake not try to take it away from you will you watch all your dreams unravel for another oh are you cold oh lost in the warmth of you the silence of you the mess in your brain that makes you think of you all your reflections in the winter night will you give up your right to say it's all for you and will you pull the thread and watch it all unravel damn it we's a baby let's go it's our song it's my song it's your song let's not stay warmth just for us and grow won't you associate the times that we knew we were both no loss no mistakes just us and thinking it's okay",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 20.3799991607666,
      "text": "Sometimes you need a little one Sometimes you need someone to pull your string",
      "start": 10.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 26.040000915527344,
      "text": "and watch you unravel inside of your own dreams to keep you honest",
      "start": 20.3799991607666
    },
    {
      "end": 33.70000076293945,
      "text": "keep you working hard to fear you can't be dishonest you can't be hard you can't lie to",
      "start": 26.920000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 43.279998779296875,
      "text": "yourself when you think you can't make it past what they won't put in front of you",
      "start": 33.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 52.91999816894531,
      "text": "are you gonna be cold are you gonna grow old and dim your lights and dim your",
      "start": 43.279998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 60.880001068115234,
      "text": "pipes and dim everything inside your right to call yourself you are you cold",
      "start": 53.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 68.31999969482422,
      "text": "you little heat inside of us all are you bold",
      "start": 62.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 80.63999938964844,
      "text": "are you cold are you bold when you pull the string and watch it all unravel",
      "start": 71.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 106.08000183105469,
      "text": "will you watch others grow not stunt not fake not try to take it away from you",
      "start": 96.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 111.80000305175781,
      "text": "will you watch all your dreams unravel for another",
      "start": 106.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 115.19999694824219,
      "text": "oh are you cold",
      "start": 113.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 124.72000122070312,
      "text": "oh lost in the warmth of you the silence of you",
      "start": 116.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 134.83999633789062,
      "text": "the mess in your brain that makes you think of you all your reflections in the winter night",
      "start": 125.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 141.52000427246094,
      "text": "will you give up your right to say it's all for you",
      "start": 136.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 152.3000030517578,
      "text": "and will you pull the thread and watch it all unravel damn it we's a baby let's go",
      "start": 142.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 161.1999969482422,
      "text": "it's our song it's my song it's your song let's not stay warmth just for us and grow",
      "start": 152.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 180.4499969482422,
      "text": "won't you associate the times that we knew we were both no loss no mistakes just us and thinking it's",
      "start": 161.47000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 181.6699981689453,
      "text": "okay",
      "start": 180.4499969482422
    }
  ],
